    <tags>blockchain cryptocurrency cli omne validator network</tags>
    <summary>Unified command-line orchestration tool for the Omne blockchain ecosystem</summary>
    <description>
The OMNE CLI provides comprehensive management for the Omne blockchain ecosystem, including:

* Network operations and management
* Validator coordination and service management  
* Infrastructure services orchestration
* Developer tools and project scaffolding
* Operational monitoring and maintenance

Features:
- Multi-network support (mainnet, testnet, devnet)
- Validator lifecycle management
- Infrastructure service deployment
- Development environment setup
- Real-time network monitoring
- Automated operational tasks
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/OmneDAO/omne-cli/releases/tag/v0.1.0</releaseNotes>
